rows.name: Thanks for beating up the scary man!

rows.label: qst006605_msg0002
rows.name:
And you're giving me a Kujinraman
Cookie too?! I'm so happy!

rows.label: qst006605_msg0003
rows.name: I'll share it with my mom!

rows.label: qst006605_msg1001
rows.name:
When I grow up, I'm going to
be a strong and kind person!

rows.label: qst006605_msg1002
rows.name:
I'll help people, then give
them a Kujinraman Cookie
and walk away coolly!
